{"tid":1672554,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李世默：西方國家應學會接受和認同中国式民主","createTime":"2019-10-24T07:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T11:08:26.000Z","uid":65371,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"dd66db48dc57327d5f6fe3e06f396ca3361debbe","tid":1672554,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/973663316341810/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393304404377707%2Fposts%2F973663316341810%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=29a85dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/973663316341810/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【李世默：西方國家應當學會接受和認同其他形式的民主】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVU8oRa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVU8oRa.jpg&h=d849a4de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日，摩洛哥新南方政策中心與法國國際關係研究所在摩洛哥馬拉喀什舉辦第12屆世界政策大會。全國政協副主席、香港特區前行政長官梁振英、中歐成為創業基金創始人及執行董事李世默、恆隆集團主席陳啟宗等出席。<br />\n<br />\n李世默在專題討論上駁斥中國沒有民主的說法，強調<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">當今世界有60多億人，西方國家人口佔10多億，為什麼只有10多億人的西方民主要獨佔全世界民主的話語權？</span></span>不同地區、國家、民族對民主有著不同定義，中國的民主解決了絕對貧困等世界難題，實現了國家的快速發展，西方國家應當學會接受和認同其他形式的民主。<br />\n<br />\n陳啟宗作為專題討論主持人，從商界角度出發並結合個人經歷表示，西方國家對中國的有色眼鏡從未摘下，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">西方國家主張「共享價值觀」，並將其強加給其他國家。這無形中在認可西方價值觀的一方和不認可的一方中劃線分割，讓人選邊站隊。</span></span>香港作為前殖民地，對此深有體會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jFrlz4yQPn7X-Lfz1EQ82Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FjFrlz4yQPn7X-Lfz1EQ82Q&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=3d1baa6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jFrlz4yQPn7X-Lfz1EQ82Q</a><br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},{"pid":"6baff8b9977976bb0374bf18faf5c3dd48e7ff34","tid":1672554,"uid":65530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9383e7b862b35951491a3e1e8f965a6877ff0999","tid":1672554,"uid":21279,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"因為人地個比例細<br />\n但你地個個都追住舔呀傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64d085b8778a6901b5828f9b2e8b8dc47a7510a","tid":1672554,"uid":242537,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"點解要接受你維尼熊中國社會主義式民主？<br />\n有核彈大撚曬？"},{"pid":"50aac5ae74d3bb1930473297bf347f30e4d7592a","tid":1672554,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d62edb25522e6d38576360e93c2f8fabadd27aa","tid":1672554,"uid":322032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"你回歸中共國再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8ef0488f9c679e441622f9a2bef665b6f0c8b9","tid":1672554,"uid":134773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"奴隸式民主?"},{"pid":"9fa6aec249899af11a8bae5787751ee22a8b0e01","tid":1672554,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:35:40.000Z","msg":"真心膠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cea588f171d6d149b5edce791f069d5b6fa92d7","tid":1672554,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"【世紀大和解】加泰集會！完美解決方案！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672540</a>"},{"pid":"e7c75f6848de253d4ee77ce3641d16f41833f395","tid":1672554,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislik